com.appglu
Interface AsyncSyncOperations

All Known Implementing Classes:
AsyncSyncTemplate
public interface AsyncSyncOperations

AsyncSyncOperations has all methods that SyncOperations has but they execute asynchronously.

Since:
1.0.0
See Also:
